        {
            "id": "action",
            "instance": "4ebbbba8-b7a9-4f2a-9b93-5d74dfe9e16d",
            "properties": [
                [
                    "name",
                    "External Remote Services"
                ],
                [
                    "ttp",
                    [
                        [
                            "tactic",
                            "TA0001"
                        ],
                        [
                            "technique",
                            "T1133"
                        ]
                    ]
                ],
                [
                    "description",
                    "External Remote Services is UFOMARKET's dominant and highest-frequency technique — the actor gains entry to victim environments exclusively via internet-facing RDP endpoints, VPN gateways, and remote management services using stolen credentials. Once inside, the foothold is validated, lateral movement is conducted via SMB, SSH, and VNC, and the resulting access is listed for sale on the UFOMARKET underground marketplace."
                ],
                [
                    "confidence",
                    null
                ],
